{"tid":454983,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成日覺得自己無人鍾意","createTime":"2017-11-01T16:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T04:55:49.000Z","uid":111596,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6bca04519a54619b8bb45385306054c6dc43ca63","tid":454983,"uid":111596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:09:45.000Z","msg":"成日覺得自己好普通 又多缺點 點解會有人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當另一半話愛你就會諗：下點解會愛 我明明咁差<br />\n就會質疑另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明唔應該咁諗<br />\n有無人都係咁..<br />\n利申非港女 只係一個自卑撚"},{"pid":"d59b60bc907a556203b230b4226687a2ecdbc961","tid":454983,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"西檸雞小妹=1234"},{"pid":"070a65e42168d2bd258ea8ccb1c266e72da34a01","tid":454983,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbbdda519068c8e70372729b61dd41f58b977fe","tid":454983,"uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"至少有人肯愛你"},{"pid":"f78e8c144d76d3c23bd399d34a2bb35558b268af","tid":454983,"uid":111596,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至少有人肯愛你</blockquote><br />\n但我會質疑..<br />\n我真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea7787bb61e91d893bab0fbd18753d484c4aee9","tid":454983,"uid":23225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:26:12.000Z","msg":"我都奇怪點會有人鐘意我<br />\n又唔靚仔又無錢性格又奇怪<br />\n所以散左之後都無信心揾到下個"},{"pid":"1526e3a3eb99bd73ebc9aa4048e6c5f2c1a9f506","tid":454983,"uid":6869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fce24077cb6fc74f5ca47d887bf18f3ec01f518","tid":454983,"uid":142378,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"repl